{"tid":1375953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線唔好當覺自己超人","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:25:21.000Z","uid":61520,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e775a7637612577c061d235bcf22c95da58373","tid":1375953,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:51:17.000Z","msg":"轉貼再發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【習慣吸毒】<br />\n<br />\n話說，有人講大家開始習慣tear gas，我想提一提到底「習慣」係代表乜野。<br />\n<br />\nTear gas係透過對刺激肺黏膜造成制衡對手，當你覺得你習慣左，其實只係好似你做野做到手生繭，你個黏膜習慣左刺激物一直存在。<br />\n<br />\n依種習慣唔係代表你進化到百毒不侵。視乎佢既成份、濃度，你既體質同重複吸入次和量，照樣有發展成長期症狀既危險性，造成肺功能惡化，產生長期影響如造成下呼吸道創傷，即破壞肺的基底膜內外皮層組織、肺氣泡等，嚴重的話也可以死人。<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好覺得係短暫可復原的攻擊。<br />\n唔該大家戴返個好d既口罩，唔好求求其其用surgical mask，最好戴返respirator。亦唔好為你習慣左而開心。<br />\n<br />\n肺係內臟有自己function，手係出面做粗重野，內傷同外傷係有重要的分別的。"},{"pid":"30797964869335621dc44286b65c32fe7cbdd85d","tid":1375953,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"咁班狗平時訓練咁多未好快死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df41780e542b80ff190675599bb5ff136e20d42e","tid":1375953,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c12c24ee41b3f4796ce6ad0cf2945b0c72d9548","tid":1375953,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375822/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[728] 需要地方落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedfb8449c350f84db4e7e8be4a06b90b5bb89e2","tid":1375953,"uid":51641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f0464d3a14edab2cdb28df08929f5cd29b2caa29","tid":1375953,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s